<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF766AC9FA7C9B261BECB692" bold="true" box="[1408,1516,3455,3488]" pageId="141" pageNumber="901">Habitat.</emphasis>
Tropical lowland forests and hill forests from sea level upto elevations of¢. 
<quantity id="036C9B1BFF766AC9F62A9B26142FB692" box="[2518,2607,3455,3488]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.0" pageId="141" pageNumber="901" unit="m" value="700.0">700 m</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
