<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF756ACAFF5E979F1D25B905" pageId="142" pageNumber="902" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF756ACAFF5E979F1D25B905" blockId="142.[159,1367,301,613]" pageId="142" pageNumber="902">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF756ACAFF5E979F1C01BAD5" bold="true" box="[162,513,454,487]" pageId="142" pageNumber="902">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Saint Aignan’s Woolly Bat is very poorly known and has not been collected since the 1950s. Studies on its ecology and threats are needed.
</paragraph>
